Siddhasiddhāntapaddhati

Edited M.L.Gharote and G.K.Pai.
Lonavla Yoga Institute 2005.

Etext input by Jim Mallinson, not complete

Corrections to jim@khecari.com



ādināthaṃ namaskṛtya śaktiyuktaṃ jagadgurum|
vakṣye gorakṣanātho 'haṃ siddhasiddhāntapaddhatim||1.1||%citation of Nityanāthakṛtasiddhasiddhāntapaddhati in GSS (p.9) gives ab followed by: taṃ vande nityato vakṣye siddhāntaṃ svānubhāvataḥ||

nāsti satyavicāre sminn utpattiś cāṇḍapiṇḍayoḥ|
tathāpi lokavṛttyarthaṃ vakṣye satsampradāyataḥ||1.2||

sā piṇḍotpattyādiḥ siddhamate samyakprasiddhā|
piṇḍotpattiḥ piṇḍavicāraḥ piṇḍasaṃvittiḥ piṇḍādhāraḥ piṇḍapadasamarasabhāvaḥ śrīnityapiṇḍāvadhūtaḥ iti||1.3||

yadā nāsti svayaṃkartā kāraṇaṃ na kulākulam|
avyaktaṃ ca paraṃ brahma anāmā vidyate tadā||1.4||

anāmeti svayam anādi siddham | ekam evānādinidhanaṃ
siddhasiddhāntaprasiddhaṃ tasyecchāmātradharmādharmiṇī nijā śaktiḥ prasiddhā||1.5||

tasyā unmukhamātreṇa parā śaktir utthitā|
tasyāḥ spandanamātreṇa aparā śaktir utthitā||1.6||

tato 'hantārthamātreṇa sūkṣmā śaktir utpannā
tato vedanaśīlā kuṇḍalinī śaktir udgatā||1.7||%vedana or vedhana??

nityatā nirañjanatā niṣpandatā nirābhāsatā nirutthānatā iti pañcaguṇā nijā śaktiḥ||1.8||

astitā aprameyatā abhinnatā anantatā avyaktatā iti pañcaguṇā parā śaktiḥ||1.9||

sphuratā sphuṭatā sphāratā sphoṭatā sphūrtitā iti pañcaguṇā aparā śaktiḥ||1.10||

niraṃśatā nirantaratā niścalatā niścayatā nirvikalpatā iti pañcaguṇā sūkṣmā śaktiḥ||1.11||

pūrṇatā pratibimbatā prabalatā proccalatā pratyaṅmukhatā iti pañcaguṇā kuṇḍalinī śaktiḥ||1.12||

evaṃ śaktitattve pañcapañcaguṇayogāt parapiṇḍotpattiḥ||1.13||

uktaṃ ca

nijā parāparā sūkṣmā kuṇḍaliny āsu pañcadhā|
śakticakrakrameṇottho jātaḥ piṇḍaḥ paraḥ śivaḥ||1.14||

aparamparaṃ paramapadaṃ śūnyaṃ nirañjanaṃ paramātmā iti||
aparamparāt sphuratāmātram utpannam|
paramapadād bhāvanāmātram utpannam|
śūnyāt sattāmātram utpannam|
nirañjanāt sākṣātkāram utpannam|
paramātmanaḥ paramātmotpannaḥ||1.15||

akalaṅkatvam anupamatvam apāratvam amūrttatvam anudayatvam
iti pañcaguṇam aparamparam||1.16||

niṣkalatvam aṇutaratvam acalatvam asaṃkhyatvam anādhāratvam
iti pañcaguṇaṃ paramapadam||1.17||

līnatā pūrṇatā unmanī lolatā mūrcchatā
iti pañcaguṇaṃ śūnyam||1.18||

satyatvaṃ sahajatvaṃ samarasatvaṃ sāvadhānatvaṃ sarvagatvam
iti pañcaguṇaṃ nirañjanam||1.19||

akṣayyatvam abhedyatvam achedyatvam adāhyatvam avināśitvam
iti pañcaguṇaḥ paramātmā||1.20||

iti anādyapiṇḍasya
pañcatattvapañcaviṃśatiguṇāḥ

uktaṃ ca

aparamparaṃ paramapadaṃ
śūnyaṃ nirañjanaparamātmanau|
pañcabhir etaiḥ saguṇair anādyapiṇḍaḥ
samutpannaḥ||1.21||

anādyāt paramānandaḥ|
paramānandāt prabodhaḥ|
prabodhāc cidudayaḥ|
cidudayāt prakāśaḥ|
prakāśāt so'hambhāvaḥ||1.22||

spando harṣa utsāho nispando nityasukhatvam iti pañcaguṇaḥ paramānandaḥ ||1.23||

udayaḥ ullāso 'vabhāso vikāsaḥ prabhā iti pañcaguṇaḥ prabodhaḥ||1.24||

sadbhāvo vicāraḥ kartṛtvaṃ jñātṛtvaṃ svatantratvaṃ iti pañcaguṇaś cidudayaḥ||1.25||

nirvikāratvaṃ niṣkalaṃkatvaṃ nirvikalpatvaṃ samatā vibhrāntir iti pañcaguṇaḥ prakāśaḥ||1.26||

ahantā'khaṇḍaiśvaryaṃ svātmatā viśvānubhavasāmarthyaṃ
sarvajñatvam iti pañcaguṇaḥ so'hambhāvaḥ||1.27||

iti ādyapiṇḍasya pañcatattvaṃ pañcaviṃśatiguṇam

uktaṃ ca

paramānandaḥ prabodhaś cidudayaś citprakāśaḥ
so'hambhāva ity anta ādyapiṇḍo mahātattvaguṇayuktaḥ
samutthitaḥ||1.28||

ādyān mahākāśo mahākāśān mahāvāyur mahāvāyor mahātejo mahātejaso mahāsalilaṃ
mahāsalilān mahāpṛthvī||1.29||

avakāśaḥ acchidratvam aspṛśatvaṃ nīlavarṇatvaṃ śabdatvam iti pañcaguṇo mahākāśaḥ||1.30||

sañcāraḥ sañcālanaṃ sparśanaṃ śoṣaṇaṃ dhrūmravarṇatvam iti pañcaguṇo mahāvāyuḥ||1.31||

dāhakatvaṃ pācakatvaṃ uṣṇatvaṃ prakāśatvaṃ raktavarṇatvam iti pañcaguṇaṃ mahātejaḥ||1.32||

pravāhaḥ āpyāyanaṃ dravo rasaḥ śvetavarṇatvam iti pañcaguṇaṃ mahāsalilam||1.33||

sthūlatā nānākāratā kāṭhinyaṃ gaṃdhaḥ pītavarṇatvam iti pañcaguṇā mahāpṛthvī||1.34||

iti mahāsākārapiṇḍasya pañcatattvaṃ pañcaviṃśatiguṇam

sa eva śivaḥ | śivād bhairavo
bhairavāc chrīkaṇṭhaḥ
śrīkaṇṭhāt sadāśivaḥ
sadāśivād īśvaraḥ
īśvarād rudraḥ
rudrād viṣṇur
viṣṇor  brahmā||1.35||

iti mahāsākārapiṇḍasya mūrtyaṣṭakam||

tadbrahmanaḥ sakāśādavalokanena naranārīrūpaḥ prakṛtipiṇḍaḥ
samutpannas tac ca pañcapañcātmakaṃ śarīram iti||1.36||

asthimāṃsatvaṅnāḍīromāṇīti pañcaguṇā bhūmiḥ||1.37||

lālā mūtraṃ śukraṃ śoṇitaṃ sveda iti pañcaguṇā āpaḥ||1.38||

kṣudhā tṛṣā nidrā kāntir ālasyam iti pañcaguṇaṃ tejaḥ||1.39||%klāntir var.

dhāvanaṃ plavanaṃ prasāraṇaṃ ākuñcanaṃ nirodhanam iti pañcaguṇo vayuḥ||1.40||

rāgo dveṣo bhayaṃ lajjā moha iti pañcaguṇa ākaśaḥ||1.41||

iti pañcaviṃśatiguṇānāṃ bhūtānāṃ prakṛtipiṇḍaḥ||

mano buddhirahaṅkāraś cittaṃ caitanyam ity antaḥkaraṇapañcakam||1.42||

saṃkalpo vikalpo mūrcchā jaḍatā mananam iti pañcaguṇaṃ manaḥ||1.43||

viveko vairāgyaṃ śāntiḥ santoṣaḥ kṣameti pañcaguṇā buddhiḥ||1.44||

abhimānaṃ madīyaṃ mama sukhaṃ mama duḥkhaṃ mamedam iti pañcaguṇo 'haṅkāraḥ||1.45||

matir dhṛtiḥ smṛtis tyāgaḥ svīkāra iti pañcaguṇaṃ cittam||1.48||

vimarśaḥ śīlanaṃ dhairyaṃ cintanaṃ nispṛhatvam iti pañcaguṇaṃ caitanyam|||1.47||

evaṃ antaḥkaraṇaguṇāḥ

sattvaṃ rajas tamaḥ kālo jīva iti kulapañcakam||1.48||

dayā dharmaḥ kriyā bhaktiḥ śraddheti pañcaguṇaṃ sattvam||1.49||

dānaṃ bhogaḥ śṛṅgāro vastugrahaṇaṃ svārthasaṃgrahaṇam iti pañcaguṇaṃ rajaḥ||1.50||

vivādaḥ kalahaḥ śoko baṃdho vañcanam iti pañcaguṇaṃ tamaḥ||1.51||

kalanā kalpanā bhrāntiḥ pramādo 'nartha iti pañcaguṇaḥ kālaḥ||1.52||

jāgrat svapnaḥ suṣuptis turyaṃ tūryātītam iti pañcāvasthāguṇo jīvaḥ||1.53||

icchā kriyā māyā prakṛtir vāg iti vyaktaśaktipañcakam||1.54||

unmādo vāsanā vāñchā cintā ceṣṭeti pañcaguṇecchā||1.55||

smaraṇam udyogaḥ kāryaṃ niścayaḥ svakulācāra iti pañcaguṇā kriyā||1.56||

mado mātsaryaṃ dambhaḥ kṛtrimatvam asatyam iti pañcaguṇā māyā||1.57||

āśā tṛṣṇā spṛhākāṃkṣā mithyeti pañcaguṇā prakṛtiḥ||1.58||

parā paśyantī madhyamā vaikharī mātṛketi pañcaguṇā vāk||1.59||

iti  vyaktiśaktipañcaviṃśatiguṇāḥ

karmaḥ kāmaś candraḥ sūryo  'gnir iti pratyakṣakaraṇapañcakam||1.60||

śubham aśubhaṃ yaśo 'pakīrtir adṛṣṭaphalasādhanam iti pañcaguṇaṃ karma||1.61||

ratiḥ prītiḥ krīḍā kāmanāturateti pañcaguṇaḥ kāmaḥ||1.63||

ullolā kallolinī uccalantī unmādinī taraṃgiṇī
śoṣiṇī alampaṭā pravṛttiḥ laharī lolā lelihānā
prasarantī pravāhā saumyā prasannā plavantī |
evaṃ candrasya ṣoḍaśa kalāḥ | saptadaśī kalā nivṛttiḥ | sā'mṛtakalā||1.63||

tāpinī grāsikā ugrā ākuñcinī śoṣiṇī prabodhinī smarā
ākarṣiṇī tuṣṭivardhinī urmirekhā kiraṇavatī prabhāvatīti
dvādaśa kalāḥ sūryasya | trayodaśī svaprakāśatā nijakalā||1.64||

dīpikā rājikā jvalanī visphuliṃginī pracaṇḍā pācikā
raudrī dāhikā rāgiṇī śikhāvatī ity
agner daśa kalāḥ | ekādaśī kalā jyotir||1.65||

iti pratyakṣakaraṇaguṇakalāsamūhaḥ

atha nāḍīnāṃ daśadvārāṇi

iḍā piṅgalā ca nāsādvārayor vahataḥ |% most mss have: suṣumnā tālumārgeṇa brahmarandhraṃ vahati | sarasvatī mukhadvāre vahati
gāndhārī hastijihvikā ca cakṣurdvārayor vahataḥ |
pūṣā yaśasvinī ca karṇadvārayor vahataḥ |
alambuṣā ānane vahati |
kuhūr gudadvāre vahati |
śaṃkhinī liṅgadvāre vahati |
suṣumṇā madhyadeśe vahati |
sā daṇḍamārgeṇa brahmarandhraparyantaṃ vahati | 

evaṃ daśanāḍyo daśadvāreṣu vahanti |
anyāḥ sarvanāḍyo romakūpeṣu vahanti ||1.66||

[atha daśavāyavaḥ]

hṛdaye prāṇavāyur ucchvāsaniḥśvāsakārako hakārasakārātmakaś ca |
gude tv apānavāyuḥ recakakumbhakapūrakaś ca |
nābhau samānavāyuḥ dīpakaḥ pācakaś ca|
kaṇṭhe vyānavāyuḥ śoṣaṇāpyāyanakārakaś ca|
tālau udānavāyuḥ grasanavamanajalpakārakaś ca|
nāgavāyuḥ sarvāṅgavyāpakaḥ mocakaś cālakaś ca|
kūrmavāyuḥ cakṣuṣor unmeṣakārakaś ca|
kṛkalaḥ udgārakaḥ kṣutkārakaś ca|
devadatto mukhavijṛmbhakaḥ|
dhanañjayo nādaghoṣakah ||1.67||

iti daśavāyvavalokanena piṇḍotpattiḥ naranārīrūpam

%added in Mallik edition (but not reported in ed - why not? Doesn't make one confident in the rest of the Ed)
%asyaivāvasthā bhede
%haṭhayoga iti saṃjñā hakāraḥ kīrtitaḥ
%sūryaṣ ṭhakāraś candra ucyate| sūryācandramaso yogāt
%kumbhakaś ca

atha garbhotthapiṇḍotpattiḥ naranārīsaṃyoge ṛtukāle

rajobindusaṃyoge jīvaḥ prathamadine kalalaṃ bhavati |
saptarātreṇa budbudākāro bhavati|
ardhamāsena golākāro bhavati |
māsamātreṇa kaṭhino bhavati|
māsadvayena śiro bhavati |
tṛtīye māsi hastapādādikaṃ bhavati|
caturthe māsi cakṣuḥkarṇādināsikāmukhameḍhragudaṃ bhavati|
pañcame māsi pṛṣṭhodaraṃ bhavati |
ṣaṣṭhe māsi nakhakeśādikaṃ bhavati|
saptame māsi sarvacetanāyukto bhavati |
aṣṭame māsi sarvalakṣaṇasaṃyukto bhavati |
navame māsi satyajñānasaṃyukto bhavati|
daśame māsi yonisaṃsparśād ajñānī bālako bhavati ||1.68||

śukrādhikye puruṣaḥ | raktādhikye kanakyā | samaśukraraktābhyāṃ
napuṃsakaḥ parasparastrīpuruṣacintāvyākulatvād andhaḥ kubjo
vāmanaḥ paṅgur aṅgahīnaś ca bhavati ||1.69||

parasparaṃ ratikāle aṅganipīḍanakaraṇaguṇaiḥ śukraṃ dvistrivāraṃ patati | tena dvitīyo bālako bhavati||1.70||

sārddhapalatrayaṃ śukraṃ, viṃśatipalaṃ raktaṃ, dvādaśapalaṃ medaḥ, daśapalaṃ majjā, śatapalaṃ māṃsaṃ, viṃśatipalaṃ śleṣmā, tadvad vātaḥ syāt | ṣaṣṭhyadhikaśatatrayam asthīny asthimātrāḥ sandhayaḥ | sārddhakoṭiromāṇi | pitṛmātṛviryaṃ  bhavati | vātapittaśleṣmadhātutrayaṃ daśadhātumayaṃ śarīram ||1.71||

iti garbhotthapiṇḍotpattiḥ%several mss have garbholi for garbhottha

iti śrīgorakṣanāthakṛtau [sic] siddhasiddhāntapaddhatau piṇḍotpattir nāma prathamopadeśaḥ [sic] ||

dvitōyopadeśaḥ

atha piṇḍavicāraḥ kathyate


piṇḍe navacakrāṇi | ādhāre brahmacakraṃ tridhāvartaṃ bhagamaṇḍalākāram | tatra mūlakandaḥ | tatra śaktiṃ pāvakākārāṃ dhyāyet | tatraiva kāmarūpapīṭhaṃ sarvakāmaphalapradaṃ bhavati ||2.1||

dvitīyaṃ svādhiṣṭhānacakram | tanmadhye paścimābhimukhaṃ
liṅgaṃ pravālāṅkurasadṛśaṃ dhyāyet | tatraivoḍyānapīṭhaṃ
jagadākarṣaṇaṃ bhavati ||2.2||

tṛtīyaṃ nābhicakraṃ pañcāvartaṃ sarpavat kuṇḍalākāram |
tanmadhye kuṇḍalinīṃ śaktiṃ bālārkakoṭisannibhāṃ
dhyāyet | sā madhyā śaktiḥ sarvasiddhidā bhavati ||2.3||

caturthaṃ hṛdayacakram aṣṭadalakamalam adhomukhaṃ tanmadhye
karṇikāyāṃ liṅgākārāṃ jyotīrūpām dhyāyet | saiva haṃsakalā sarvendriyavaśyā bhavati ||2.4||

pañcamaṃ kaṇṭhacakraṃ caturaṅgulam | tatra vāma iḍā candranāḍī |
dakṣiṇe piṅgalā sūryanāḍī | tanmadhye suṣumnāṃ
dhyāyet | saiva anāhatakalā anāhatasiddhidā bhavati ||2.5||

ṣaṣṭhaṃ tālucakram | tatrāmṛtadhārāpravāhaḥ | ghaṃṭikāliṅgaṃ
mūlarandhraṃ rājadantaṃ śaṃkhinīvivaraṃ daśamadvāram |
tatra śūnyaṃ dhyāyet | cittalayo bhavati ||2.6||

saptamaṃ bhrūcakraṃ madhyamāṅguṣṭhamatram | tatra jñānanetraṃ dīpaśikhākāraṃ dhyāyet | tatra vāksiddhir bhavati ||2.7||

aṣṭamaṃ brahmarandhraṃ nirvāṇacakraṃ sūcikāgrabhedyam | tatra
dhūmaśikhākāraṃ dhyāyet | tatra jālandharapīṭhaṃ mokṣapradaṃ
bhavati ||2.8||

navamam ākāśacakraṃ soḍaśadalakamalam ūrdhvamukham |
tanmadhye karṇikāyāṃ trikūṭākārāṃ tadūrdhvaśaktiṃ
tāṃ paramaśunyāṃ dhyāyet | tatraiva pūrṇagiripīṭhaṃ sarveṣṭasiddhir bhavati ||2.9||

iti navacakravicāraḥ ||

atha ṣoḍaśādhārāḥ kathyante |

tatra prathamaḥ pādāṅguṣṭhādhāraḥ | tatrāgratas tejomayaṃ
dhyāyet | dṛṣṭiḥ sthirā bhavati ||2.10||

dvitīyo mūlādhāras taṃ vāmapādapārṣṇinā
niṣpīḍya sthātavyam | tatrāgnidīpanaṃ bhavati ||2.11||

tṛtīyo gudādhāra taṃ vikāsasaṃkocanena nirākuñcayet |
apānavāyuḥ sthiro bhavati ||2.12||

caturtho meḍhrādhāraḥ | liṅgasaṃkocanena brahmagranthitrayaṃ
bhitvā bhramaraguhāyāṃ viśramya tata ūrdhvamukhe
bindustambhanaṃ bhavati| eṣā vajrolī prasiddhā ||2.13||

pañcame oḍīyāṇādhārayor bandhanān malamūtrasaṃkocanaṃ
bhavati||2.14||%uḍyānā° etc. in various mss

ṣaṣṭhe nābhyādhāra oṃkāram ekacittenoccārayet |
nādalayo bhavati ||2.15||

saptame hṛdayādhāre prāṇaṃ nirodhayet | kamalavikāso
bhavati ||2.16||

aṣṭame kaṇṭhādhāre kaṇṭhamūlaṃ cibukena nirodhayet |
iḍāpiṅgalayor vāyuḥ sthiro bhavati ||2.17||

navame ghaṇṭikādhāre jihvāgraṃ dhārayet | amṛtakalā
sravati ||2.18||

daśame tālvādhāre tālvantargarbhe lambikāṃ cālanadohanābhyāṃ
dīrghīkṛtvā viparītena praveśayet | kāṣṭhībhavati||2.19 ||

ekādaśe atha jihvādhāre tatra jihvāgraṃ dhārayet | sarvaroganāśo
bhavati ||2.20||

dvādaśe bhrūmadhyādhāre tatra candramaṇḍalaṃ dhyāyet
śītalatāṃ yāti ||2.21||

trayodaśe nāsādhāre tasyāgraṃ lakṣayet
manaḥ sthiraṃ bhavati ||2.22||

caturdaśe nāsāmūle kapāṭādhāre dṛṣṭiṃ dhārayet |
ṣaṇmāsāj jyotiḥpuñjaṃ paśyati ||2.23||

pañcadaśe lalāṭādhāre tatra jyotiḥpuñjaṃ lakṣayet |
tejasvī bhavati ||2.24||

avaśiṣṭe ṣoḍaśe brahmarandhram ākāśacakram | tatra
śrīgurucaraṇāmbujayugmaṃ sadāvalokayet | ākāśavat pūrṇo bhavati ||2.25||

iti ṣoḍaśādhāraḥ  ||

atha lakṣatrayam

tatra tāvad antarlakṣyaṃ kathyate 

mūlakandād daṇḍalagnāṃ brahmanāḍīṃ śvetavarṇāṃ
brahmarandhraparyantaṃ gatāṃ saṃsmaret |
tanmadhye kamalatantunibhāṃ vidyutkoṭiprabhām ūrdhvagāminīṃ
tāṃ mūrtiṃ manasā lakṣayet | sarvasiddhipradā bhavati ||2.26|| % checked to here from 2.10

athavā lalāṭordhve kollāṭamaṇḍape sphuratkārākāraṃ
lakṣayet| athavā bhramaraguhāmadhye āraktabhramarākāraṃ
lakṣayed athavā karṇadvayaṃ tarjanībhyāṃ nirodhayet tataḥ
śiromadhye dhūṃ dhūṃ kāraṃ nādaṃ śṛṇoti athavā cakṣurmadhye
nīlajyotirūpaṃ putalyākāraṃ lakṣayed ity antarlakṣyam||2.27||

nāsāgrāt bahiraṅgulacatuṣṭaye nīlajyotiḥsaṃkāśaṃ
lakṣayet| athavā nāsāgrāt ṣaḍaṅgula adhovāyutatvaṃ dhūmravarṇaṃ
lakṣayed athavā aṣṭāṅgule āraktaṃ tejastatvaṃ lakṣayet athavā
daśāṅgule kallolavadāpastatvaṃ lakṣayet| athavānāsāgrāt
dvādaśāṅgule pītavarṇaṃ pārthivatatvaṃ lakṣayed athavā
ākāśamukhaṃ dṛṣṭvāvalokayet kiraṇānākulitaṃ paśyati evaṃ
nirmalīkaraṇam| athavordhvadṛṣṭayāntarālaṃ lakṣayet jyotirmukhāni
paśyati athavā yatra tatrākāśaṃ lakṣayed ākāśasadṛśaṃ cittaṃ
muktipradaṃ bhavati athavā dṛṣṭyānatas taptakāṃcanasaṃnibhāṃ
bhūmiṃ lakṣayet dṛṣṭiḥ sthirā bhavati|
ity anekavidhaṃ bahirlakṣyam||2.28||

śvetavarṇaṃ vā raktavarṇaṃ vā kṛṣṇavarṇaṃ vā
agniśikhākāraṃ vā jyotirūpaṃ vā vidyudākāraṃ
sūryamaṇḍalākāraṃ vā arddhacandrākāraṃ vā
yatheṣṭasvapiṇḍamātraṃ sthānavarjitaṃ manasā lakṣayet
ityanekaviddhaṃ madhyamaṃ lakṣyaṃ||2.29||

ākāśaṃ parākāśaṃ mahākāśaṃ tatvākaśaṃ
sūryākāśamiti vyomapañcakam| bāhyābhyantare 'tyantaṃ
nirmalaṃ nirākāraṃ ākāśaṃ lakṣayet|
athavā bāhyābhyantare 'tyantāndhakāranibhaṃ
parākāśam avalokayet| bāhyābhyantare kālānalasaṃkāśaṃ
mahākāśam avalokayet|
bāhyābhyantare nijatatvakharūpaṃ tatvākāśam avalokayet|
athavā bāhyābhyantare sūryakoṭisadṛśaṃ sūryākāśam avalokayet|
evaṃ vyomapañcakāvalokanena vyomasadṛśo bhavati||2.30||

navacakraṃ kalādhāraṃ trilakṣyaṃ vyomapañcakam|cf.NT 7.1
samyag etan na jānāti sa yogī nāmadhārakaḥ||2.31||

yamaniyamāsanaprāṇāyāmapratyāhāradhāraṇādhyānasamādhayoḥ
'ṣṭāṅgāni| yama iti upaśamaḥ sarvendriyajayaḥ
āhāranidrāśītavātātapajayaś caivaṃ śanaiḥ śanai
sādhayet||2.32||

niyama iti manovṛttīnāṃ niyamanam iti ekāntavāso
niḥsaṃgataudāsīnyaṃ yathāprāptisaṃtuṣṭir vairasyaṃ
gurucaraṇāvarūḍhatvam iti niyamalakṣaṇam||2.33||

āsanam iti svasvarūpe samāsannatā| svastikāsanaṃ padmāsanaṃ
siddhāsanam eteṣāṃ madhye yatheṣṭam ekaṃ vidhāya sāvadhānena
sthātavyam ity āsanalakṣaṇam||2.34||

prāṇāyāma iti prāṇasya sthiratā
recakapūrakakumbhakasaṃghaṭṭakaraṇāni catvāri
prāṇāyāmalakṣaṇam||2.35||

pratyāhāram iti caitanyataraṅgānāṃ pratyāharaṇaṃ yathā
nānāvikāragrasanotpannavikārasyāpi nivṛttiḥ
nirbhātīti pratyāhāralakṣaṇam||2.36||

dhāraṇeti sabāhyābhyantara ekam eva nijatatvasvarūpam evāntaḥkaraṇena
sādhayet yathā yadyad utpadyate tattan nirākāre dhārayet
svātmānaṃ nirvātadipam iva dhārayed iti dhāraṇalakṣaṇam||2.37||

atha dhyānam iti ||
asti kaś cana paramādvaitasya bhāvaḥ
sa eva ātmeti yathā yadyat sphurati tattat svarūpam eveti bhāvayet
sarvabhūteṣu samadṛṣṭiś ceti dhyānalakṣaṇam||2.38||

atha samādhilakṣaṇam| sarvatatvānāṃ samāvasthā
nirudyamatvam anāyāsasthitimattvam iti samādhilakṣaṇam||2.39||

3.1 piṇḍamadhye carācarau yo jānāti sa yogī
piṇḍasaṃvittir bhavati||

3.2 kūrmaḥ pādatale vasati pātālaṃ pādāṅguṣṭhe
talātalam aṅguṣṭhāgre mahātalaṃ pṛṣṭhe rasātalaṃ
hulphe sutalaṃ jaṅghāyāṃ vitalaṃ jānvoḥ
atalam urvor evaṃ saptapātālaṃ rudradevatādhipatye tiṣṭhati
piṇḍamadhye krodharūpī bhāvaḥ
sa eva kālāgnirudraḥ
mahātalaṃ pādapṛṣthe

3.3 bhūrlokaṃ guhyasthāne bhuvarlokaṃ liṅgasthāne
svarlokaṃ nābhisthāne evaṃ lokatraye indro devatā
piṇḍamadhye sarvendriyaniyāmakaḥ
sa evendraḥ||

3.4 daṇḍāṅkure maharlokaḥ daṇḍakuhare jano lokaḥ
daṇḍanāle tapo lokaḥ mūlakamale satyalokaḥ evaṃ
lokacatuṣṭaye brahmādidevatā piṇḍamadhye
anekamānābhimānasvarūpī tiṣṭhati||

3.5 viṣṇulokaḥ kukṣau tiṣṭhati tatra viṣṇur devatā
piṇḍamadhye aṇekavyāpārakārako bhavati|
hṛdaye rudralokaḥ tatra rudro devatā piṇḍamadhye
ugrasvarūpī tiṣṭhati| vakṣaḥsthale īśvaralokaḥ
tatra īśvaro devatā piṇḍamadhye tṛptisvarūpī tiṣṭhati|
kaṇṭhamadhye nīlakaṇṭho lokas tatra nīlakaṇṭho
devatā piṇḍamadhye nityaṃ tiṣṭhati|
tāludvāre śivalokas tatra śivo devatā piṇḍamadhye
'nupamasvarūpī tiṣṭhati| lambikāmūle
bhairavalokastatra bhairavo devatā piṇḍamadhye
sarvottamasvarūpī tiṣṭhati| lalāṭamadhye
'nādilokastatrānādidevatā piṇḍamadhye
ānandaparāhantāsvarūpī tiṣṭhati|
śṛṅgāre
kulalokas tatra kuleśvaro
devatā piṇḍamadhye ānandasvarūpī tiṣṭhati|
śaṃkhamadhye nalinīsthāne
akuleśvaro devatā
piṇḍamadhye nirabhimānāvasthā tiṣṭhati|
brahmarandhre parabrahmalokas tatra parabrahma devatā
piṇḍamadhye paripūrṇadaśā tiṣṭhati|
ūrdhvakamale parāparalokas tatra parameśvaro
devatā piṇḍamadhye parāparabhāvas tiṣṭhati|
trikūṭasthāne śaktilokas tatra parāśaktir devatā
sarvasaṃ sarvakartṛtvāvasthā tiṣṭhati|
evaṃ piṇḍamadhye
saptapātālasahitaikaviṃśatibrahmāṇḍasthānavicāraḥ

3.6 sadācāratatve brāhmaṇāḥ vasanti śaurye kṣatriyāḥ
vyavasāye vaiśyāḥ sevābhāve śūdrāś catuṣaṣṭikalāsv api
catuḥṣaṣṭivarṇāḥ

3.7 majjāyaṃ jambūdvīpaḥ asthiṣu śaktidvīpaḥ
śirāsu sūkṣmadvīpaḥ tvakṣu krauñcadvīpaḥ
romasu gomayadvīpaḥ nakheṣu śvetadvīpaḥ
māṃse (asthini) plakṣadvīpaḥ
evaṃ saptadvīpāḥ

3.8 mūrte kṣārasamudraḥ lālāyāṃ kṣīrasamudraḥ
kaphe dadhisamudraḥ medasi ghṛtasamudraḥ vasāyāṃ
madhusamudraḥ rakte ikṣusamudraḥ śukre 'mṛtasamudraḥ
evaṃ saptasamudrāḥ||

3.9 navakhaṇḍāḥ nava dvāreṣu vasanti|
bhāratakhaṇḍaḥ kāśmīrakhaṇḍaḥ karparakhaṇḍaḥ śrīkhaṇḍaḥ
śaṅkhakhaṇḍaḥ ekapādakhaṇḍaḥ gāndhārakhaṇḍaḥ
kaivartakhaṇḍaḥ mahāmerukhaṇḍaḥ evaṃ navakhaṇḍāḥ

meruparvato merukhaṇḍe vasati kailāso brahmakapāṭe vasati
himālayaḥ pṛṣṭhe malayo vāmakandhare mandaro dakṣiṇakandhare
vindhyo dakṣiṇakarṇe mainākaḥ vāmakarṇe śrīparvato lalāṭe
evam aṣṭa kulaparvatāḥ anye upaparvatāḥ sarvāṅguliṣu vasanti3.10||

pīnasā gaṅgā yamunā candrabhāgā sarasvatī|
pipāsā śatarudrā ca śrīrātriś caiva narmadā evaṃ nava
nadyo navanāḍīṣu vasanti||3.11||

anyā upanadyaḥ kulyopakulyāḥ dvisaptati
sahasra nāḍīsu vasanti||3.12||

saptaviṃśatinakṣatrāṇi dvādaśa rāśayaḥ
nava grahāḥ pañcadaśa tithayaḥ ete antarvalaye
dvisaptati sahasra svahastakoṣṭheṣu vasanti|
anekatāramaṇḍalaṃ ūrmiṣu vasanti|
trayastriṃśatkoṭidevatā bāhuromakūpeṣu vasanti|
anekapīṭḥopapīṭhakāḥ romakūpeṣu vasanti|
devadānavayakṣarākṣasapiśācabhūtapretāḥ
asthisandhiṣu vasanti| kulanāgā vakṣasi vasanti|
anye sanakādimunisaṃdhāḥ kakṣaromakūpeṣu vasanti|
anye parvatā udaralomasu vasanti|
gandharvakinnarakiṃpuruṣā apsaraso gaṇā udare vasanti|
anyāḥ khecarīlīlāmātaraḥ śaktayaḥ ugradevatā
vāyuvege vasanti| anekameghāḥ aśrupāte vasanti|
anekatīrthāni marmasthāne vasanti| anantasiddhāḥ  matiprakaśe
vasanti| candrasūryau netradvaye vasataḥ| anekavṛkṣalaṭāgulmatṛṇāni
jaṅghāromakakūpasthāne vasanti| anekakṛmikīṭapataṅgāḥ
purīṣe vasanti||3.13||

yat sukhaṃ tat svargaṃ yad duḥkhaṃ tan narakaṃ
yat karma tad bandhanaṃ yan nirvikalpaṃ tan muktiḥ
svasvarūpadaśāyāṃ nidrādau svātmajāgaraḥ
śāntir bhavati| evaṃ sarvadeheṣu viśvasvarūpaḥ
parameśvaraḥ paramātmā akhaṇḍasvabhāvena ghaṭe ghaṭe
citsvarūpī tiṣṭhati||3.14||

4.1 asti kācid aparamparā saṃvitsvarūpā
sarvapiṇḍādhāratvena nityaprabuddhā nijā śaktiḥ
prasiddhā kāryakāraṇa kataṇāmutthānadaśāṅkuronmīlanena
kartāraṃ karoti ata evādhāraśaktir iti kathyate|
atyantaṃ
nijaprakāśasvasaṃvedānubhavaikyagamyamānaśāstralaukikasākṣātkārasākṣiṇī
sā parācidrūpiṇī śaktir gīyate| saiva śaktir yadā sahajena
svāsminn unmīlinyāṃ nirutthānadaśāyaṃ vartate tadā śivaḥ
saiva bhavati|

4.2 ata eva kulākulasvarūpā sāmarasyanijabhūmikā nigadyate||

4.3 kulam iti| parāsattahantāsphurattakalāsvarūpeṇa saiva
pañcadhā viśvasyādhāratvena tiṣṭhati
parābhāsatvād ahantā sattā

4.4 ata eva parāparā nirābhāsāvabhāsakāt
prakāśasvarūpā yā sā parā

4.5 anādisaṃsiddhā paramādvaitaparamekamevāstiti
yā aṅgīkāraṃ karoti sā sattā||

4.6 anādinidhano 'prameyasvabhāvaḥ kiraṇānando
śmyahamityahaṃsūcanaśīlā ya sā parāhantā||

4.7 svānubhavacittacamatkāranirutthānadaśāṃ prasphuṭī
karoti yā sā sphurattā||

4.8 nityaśuddhabuddhasvarūpasya svayaṃ prakāśatvam akalayatīti
yā sā parākaleti ucyate

4.9 akulam iti|jātivarṇagotrādyakhilanimittatvenaikam evāstīti
prasiddha|
niruttare 'nanyatvādakhaṇḍatvādananyāśrayatvādnirdhāmatvādanāmatvādakulaṃ
syānniruttaramiti

evaṃ kulākulasāmarasyaprakāśabhūmikāsphuṭīkaraṇe ekaiva
samarthā yā sā aparamparā śaktirevāvaśiṣyate|
aparamparaṃ nikhilaviśvaprapañcajālaṃ paraṃ tattvaṃ
sampādayatyekīkarotyaparāmparā?śaktirāśāvatī prasiddhā4.10||

akulaṃ kulam ādhatte kulaṃ cākulam icchati|
jalabudbudavad nyāyād ekākāraḥ paraḥ śivaḥ4.11||

ata evaikākāra evānantaśaktimān nijānandatayāvasthito
'pi nānākāratvena vilasan svapratiṣṭhāṃ svayam eva
bhajatīti vyavahāraḥ|
aluptaśaktimān nityaṃ sarvākāratayā sphuran|
punaḥ svenaiva rūpeṇa eka evāvaśiṣyate||4.12||

ata eva paramakāraṇaṃ parameśvaraḥ śivaḥ svarūpatayā sarvatomukhaḥ
sarvākāratayā sphurituṃ śaknotītyataḥ śaktimān|
śivo 'pi śaktirahitaḥ śaktaḥ kartuṃ na kiñcana|
svaśaktyā sahitaḥ so 'pi sarvasyābhāsako bhavet||4.13||

ata evānantaśaktimān parameśvaraḥ viśvasaṃvitsvarūpī viśvamayo
bhavatīti prasiddhaṃ siddhānāṃ ca parāparasvarūpā kuṇḍalinī
vartate| atas te piṇḍasiddhāḥ prasiddhāḥ| sā kuṇḍalinī
prabuddhāprabuddhā ceti dvidhā| aprabuddheti tattatpiṇḍe cetanarūpā
(svabhāvena nānācintāvyāpārodyamaprapañcarūpā) kuṭilasvabhāvā
kuṇḍalinī khyātā| saiva yogināṃ tattadvilasitavikārāṇāṃ
nivāraṇodyamasvarūpā kuṇḍaliny ūrdhvagāminī
suprasiddhā bhavati 4.14||

ūrdhvamiti| sarvatattvāny api svasvarūpam evety ūrdhve vartate
ata eva sā vimarśarūpiṇī yoginaḥ svasvarūpam avagacchantīti
suprasiddhā||4.15||

tathā coktam eve rulake:

madhyaśaktiprabodhena adhaḥśaktinikuñcanāt|
ūrdhvaśaktinipātena prāpyate paramaṃ padam||4.16||

ekaiva sā madhyordhvādhaḥ prabhedena tridhā bhinnā śaktir
abhidhīyate ||4.17||

bāhyendriyavyāpāranānācintāmayī saivādhaḥśaktir ity ucyate|
ata eva yoginas tasyā ākuñcane ratāḥ | asyā ākuñcanaṃ mūlādhārabandhanāt siddhaṃ
syāt | yasmāc carācaraṃ jagad idaṃ cidacidātmakaṃ
prabhavati | sa eva mūlādhāraḥ saṃvitprasaraḥ prasiddhaḥ ||4.18||

uktaṃ śivānandācāryaiḥ:

sarvaśaktiprasarasaṃkocābhyāṃ jagatsṛṣṭiḥ
saṃhṛtiś ca bhavaty eva na saṃdehaḥ | tasmāt tāṃ
mūlam ity ucyate| ataḥ prāyeṇa sarve siddhāḥ
mūlādhāraratā bhavanti ||4.19||

taraṅgitasvabhāvaṃ jīvātmānaṃ vṛthā bhramantam api
svaprakāśamadhye svasvarūpatayā sarvadā dhārayituṃ
samarthā yā sā madhyā śaktiḥ kuṇḍalinī
gīyate| sthūlasūkṣmarūpeṇa mahāsiddhānāṃ pratīyate
iti niścayaḥ||4.20||

sthūleti nikhilagrāhyādhāragrāhyasvarūpāpi
padārthāntarair bhrāmyamāṇā cidrūpā yā vartate sā
kuṇḍalinī sākārā sthūlā || punas tv iyam eva svaprasāracāturyatayā
vartamānā yogināṃ parānandadāyinī kuṇḍalinī yā niścayabhūtā
vartate sā sūkṣmā nirākārā prabuddhā mahāsiddhānāṃ
mate prasiddhā ||4.21||

uktaṃ tantrasāre —

sṛṣṭiḥ kuṇḍalinī khyātā dvidhā bhāvagatā tu sā|
ekadhā sthūlarūpā ca lokānāṃ pratyagātmikā ||4.22||

aparā sarvagā sūkṣmā vyāptivyāpakavarjitā|
tasyā bhedaṃ na jānāti mohitaḥ pratyayena tu ||4.23||

tasmāt sūkṣmā parā saṃvitsvarūpā madhyā śaktiḥ
kuṇḍalinī yogibhir dehasiddhyarthaṃ sadgurumukhāj jñātvā
svasvarūpadaśāyāṃ prabodhanīyā ||4.24||

athaordhvaśaktinipātaḥ kathyate —

sarveṣāṃ tattvānām upari vartamānatvān nirnāma
paramapadam evordhvam iti prasiddham | tasya
svasaṃvedananānāsākṣātkārasūcanaśīlā yā sā
ūrdhvaśaktir abhidhīyate | tasyāḥ nipātanam iti
svasvarūpadvidhābhāsanirābhāsamātraṃ na kiṃ tu svasvarūpākhaṇḍatvena
bhavati ||4.25||

uktaṃ ca

śivasyābhyantare śaktiḥ śakter abhyantaraḥ śivaḥ|
antaraṃ naiva jānīyāc candracandrikayor iva ||4.26||

ata ūrdhvaśaktinipātena mahāsiddhayogibhiḥ
paramaṃ padaṃ prāpyate iti siddham ||4.27||

sattve sattve sakalaracanā rājate saṃvid ekā|
tattve tattve paramamahimā saṃvid evāvamāti||4.28||

bhāve bhāve bahula taralā lampaṭā saṃvid eṣā|
bhāse bhāse bhajanacaturā bṛṃhitā saṃvid eva||4.29||

kim uktaṃ bhavati parāparavimarśarūpiṇī saṃvinānāśaktirūpeṇa
nikhilapiṇḍādhāratvena vartate iti siddhāntaḥ ||4.30||

5.1 mahāsiddhayogibhiḥ pūrvoktakrameṇa parapiṇḍādisvapiṇḍāntaṃ
jñātvā paramapade samarasaṃ kuryāt||

5.2 paramapadam itisvasaṃvedyaṃ atyantābhāsābhāsakamayam||

5.3 yatra buddhir mano nāsti tattvavin nāparā kalā|
ūhāpohau na kartavyau vācā tatra karoti kim||
vāgminā guruṇa samyak kathaṃ tatpadam īyate|
tasmād uktaṃ śivenaiva svasaṃvedyaṃ paraṃ padam||

5.4 ata eva nānāviddhavicāryacāturya vacasā vismayāṃ gatvā
gurucaraṇaratatvāt nirṇītatvāt svasaṃvedyameva paramaṃ padaṃ
prasiddham itisiddhāntaḥ
kṛpātatvamātreṇa \ha gurucaraṇatvāt nirupādhikatvāt

5.5 gurur atra samyak sanmārgadarśanaśīlo bhavati|
sanmārgo yogamārgas taditaraḥ pāṣaṇḍamārgaḥ|
yogamārgeṣu tantreṣu dīkṣitāṃś ca(?) dūṣakāḥ|
te hi pāṣaṇḍinaḥ proktāḥ tathā taiḥ sahavāsinaḥ

5.6 yasmin darśite sati tatkṣaṇāt svasaṃvedyasākṣātkāraḥ samutpadyate|
tato gurur evātra kāraṇam ucyate||

5.7 tasmād gurukaṭākṣapātāt svasaṃvedyatayā ca mahāsiddhayogibhiḥ
svakīyaṃ piṇḍaṃ nirutthānānubhavena samarasaṃ kriyate iti siddhāntaḥ||

5.8 mahāsiddhayoginaḥ svasvarūpatayānusandhānena nijāveśo bhavati
nijāveśān nipīḍitanirutthānadaśāmahodayaḥ kaś cij jāyate|
tataḥ saccidānandacamatkārāt adbhutākāraprakāśaprabodho jāyate|
prabodhād akhilam etad dvayādvayaprakaṭatayā caitanyabhāsābhāsakaṃ parātparaṃ
pdameva prasphuṭaṃ bhavatīti satyam

5.9 ata eva mahāsiddhayogibhiḥ samyak (ukta) guruprasādaṃ labdhvāvadhānabalenaikyaṃ
bhajamānais tatkṣaṇāt paramaṃ padam evānubhūyate||

tadanubhavabalena svakīyaṃ siddhaṃ samyak nijapiṇḍaṃ parijñātvā
tam eva paramapade ekīkṛtya tasmin pratyāvṛtyārūḍhevābhyantare
svapiṇḍasiddhyarthaṃ mahattvam anubhūyate||5.10||

nijapiṇḍam iti svarūpakiraṇānandonmeṣamātraṃ yasyonmeṣasya
pratyāharaṇam eva samarasakaraṇaṃ bhavati5.11||

ata eva svakīyaṃ piṇḍaṃ mahāraśmipuñjaṃ
svenaivākāreṇa pratīyamānaṃ svānusaṃdhānena
svasminnurarīkṛtya mahāsiddhayoginaḥ piṇḍasiddhyarthaṃ
tiṣṭhantīti prasiddham||5.12||

śaṃkhamudrādhāraṇaṃ ca keśaromapradhāraṇam|
amarīpānam amalaṃ tathā mardanam utkaṭam5.13||

ekāntavāso dīkṣā ca saṃdhyājapamāśrayā|
jhāna(?)bhairavamūrtes tu tatpūjā ca surādibhiḥ
japamamāyayā \ha5.14||

śaṅkhādhmātaṃ siṃhanādaṃ kaupīnaṃ pādukā tathā|
aṅgavastraṃ bahirvastraṃ kambalaṃ chatramadhutam||5.15||

vetraṃ kamaṇḍaluṃ caiva bhasmanā ca tripuṇḍrakam|
kuryād etān prayatnena guruvandanapūrvakam||5.16||

teṣāṃ piṇḍasiddhau satyāṃ sarvasiddhayaḥ sannidhānā bhavanti||5.17||

yasmin jñāte jagat sarvaṃ siddhaṃ bhavati līlayā|
siddhayaḥ svayam āyānti tasmād jñeyaṃ paraṃ padam||5.18||

paraṃ padaṃ na veṣeṇa prāpyate paramārthataḥ|
dehamūlaṃ hi veṣaṃ syāl lokapratyayahetukam||5.19||

loke nikṛṣṭam utkṛṣṭaṃ parigṛhya pṛthakkṛtam|
tatsvadharma iti prokto yogamārge viśeṣataḥ||5.20||

yogamārgāt paro mārgo nāsti nāsti śrutau smṛtau||5.21||

śāstreṣv anyeṣu sarveṣu śivena kathitaḥ purā|
yogaḥ sannahanopāyo jñānasaṃgatiyuktiṣu
5.23 loke nikṛṣ'ṃ satataṃ yaṃ vā yaṃ vā prakurvato|
taṃ vā taṃ vā varjayanti yogajñānabalena tu||5.22||

manuṣyāṇāṃ ca sarveṣāṃ prāksaṃskāravaśād iha|
śāstrayuktisamācāraḥ krameṇa bhavati sphuṭam||5.24||

evaṃ piṇḍe saṃsiddhe jñānaprāptyarthaṃ tac ca paramapadaṃ
mahāsiddhānāṃ mataṃ parijñāya tasminn ahambhāve jīvātmā ca
sahajasaṃyamasopāyādvaitakrameṇopalakṣyate||5.25||

tatra sahajam iti| viśvātītaṃ parameśvaraṃ viśvarūpeṇāvabhāsamānam iti
ekam evāstīti svasvabhāvena yadjñānaṃ tatsahajaṃ prasiddham||5.26||

saṃyama iti| sāvadhānānāṃ prasphuradvyāpārāṇāṃ nijavṛttīnāṃ
saṃyamanaṃ kṛtvā ātmani dhīyate iti saṃyamaḥ||5.27||

sopāyamiti| svayam eva prakāśamayaṃ svenaiava svātmany ekīkṛtya
sadā tattvena sthātavyam||5.28||

advaitam iti| akartṛtayaiva yogī nityatṛpto nirvikalpaḥ sadā
nirutthānatvena tiṣṭhati||5.29||

sahajaṃ svātmasaṃvittiḥ saṃyamaḥ svātmanigrahaḥ|
sopāyaḥ svasya viśrāntir advaitaṃ paramaṃ padam5.30||

taj jñeyaṃ sadguror vaktrāt nānyathā śāstrakoṭibhir|
na tarkaśabdavijñānān nācārād vedapāṭhanāt5.31||

vedāntaśravaṇān naiva tattvamasyādibodhanāt|
na haṃsoccāraṇāj jīvabrahmaṇor aikyabhāvanāt||5.32||

na dhyānān na layāl līnaḥ sarvajñaḥ siddhipāragaḥ|
sveccho yogī svayaṃkartā līlayā cājaro 'maraḥ5.33||

avadhyo devadaityānāṃ krīḍate bhairavo yathā|
ity evaṃ niścalo yo 'sau kramād āpnoti līlayā||5.34||

asādhyāḥ siddhayaḥ sarvaḥ satyam īśvarabhāsitam|
prathame tv arogatāsiddhiḥ sarvalokapriyo bhavet|
kaṃkṣate darśanaṃ tasya svātmārūḍhsya nityaśaḥ5.35||

kṛtārthaḥ syād dvitīye tu kurute sarvabhāṣyā|
tṛtīye divyadehas tu vyālair vyāghrair na bādhyate5.36||

caturthe kṣuttṛṣānidrāśītatāpavivarjitaḥ|
jāyate divyayogīśo dūraśrāvī na saṃśayaḥ||5.37||

vāksiddhiḥ pañcame varṣe parakāyapraveśanam|
ṣaṣṭhe na chidyate śastrair vajrapātair na bādhyate||5.38||

vāyuvegī kṣtityāgī dūradarśī ca saptame|
aṇimādiguṇopetas tv aṣṭame vatsare bhavet5.39||

navame vajrakāyaḥ syāt khecaro dikcaro bhavet|
daśame pavanād vegī yatrecchā tatra dhāvati||5.40||

samyag ekādaśe varṣe sarvajñaḥ siddhibhāg bhavet|
dvādaśe śivatulyo 'sau kartā hartā svayaṃ bhavet||5.41||

trailokye pūjyate siddhaḥ satyaṃ śrībhairavo yathā|
evaṃ dvādaśavarṣeṣu siddhayogī mahābalaḥ||
jāyate sadguroḥ pādaprabhāvān nātra saṃśayaḥ||5.42||

gurukulasantānaṃ ceti pañcadhā proktam| āīsantānaṃ
vileśvarasantānaṃ vibhūtisantānaṃ nāthasantānaṃ
yogīśvarasantānaṃ ceti eṣām api santānānāṃ pṛthak pṛthak
vaiśiṣṭyaṃ vartate||5.43||

 paramārthataḥ sava pañcabhautikam| tajjātāḥ puruṣāḥ|
(svavogha) sambodhamātraikarūpaḥ saśivaḥ|
taditarat sarvam ajñānam avyaktaṃ bhavati tatra śivas tu
jñānam5.44||

eteṣām api santānānāṃ ke cit svarūpaparāṅmukhāḥ
veṣamātrasampannāḥ krayavikrayādikaṃ kurvanti
santānabhedaṃ pratyanyo 'nyam adhaḥ kurvanti
yogamārgaṃ dveṣayanti||5.45||

rajasā ghorasaṃkalpāḥ kāmukāḥ atimanyavaḥ|
dāmbhikāḥ māninaḥ pāpāḥ dhik kurvanty īśvarapriyān5.46||

sādhusaṃgamasacchāstraparamānandalakṣitān|
svecchācāravihāraikajñānavijñānasaṃyutān||5.47||

yūyaṃ duṣṭā vayaṃ śiṣtā bhraṣṭā yūyaṃ vayaṃ tathyāḥ|
ity evaṃ parivadanti sampramohe nirantaram5.48||

pṛthvī jalaṃ tathā vahniḥ vāyur ākāśam eva ca|
ete santānodayās tu samyag eva prakīrtitāḥ||5.49||

kāṭhinyaṃ cārdratā tejo dhāvanaṃ sthiratā khalu|
guṇāny etāni pañcaiva santānānāṃ kramāt smṛtāḥ||5.50||

brahmā viṣṇuś ca rudraś ca īśvaraś ca sadāśivaḥ|
etāś ca devatāḥ proktāḥ santānānāṃ krameṇa tu||5.51||

sthūlasūkṣmakāraṇaṃ tūryaṃ tūryātītam iti pañcāvasthāḥ
krameṇa lakṣyante| eteṣām api sarveṣāṃ vijñātā yaḥ sa yogī
sa siddhapuruṣaḥ sa yogīśvareśvara iti paramarahasyaṃ prakāśitam||5.52||

ata eva samyak nijaviśrāntikārakaṃ mahāyoginaṃ sadguruṃ
sevayitvā samyak sāvadhānena paramaṃ padaṃ sampādya tasmin
nijapiṇḍe (piṇḍaṃ) samarasabhāvaṃ kṛtvātyantaṃ nirutthānena
sarvānandatattve niścalaṃ sthātavyam | tataḥ svayam eva mahāsiddho
bhavatīti satyam||5.53||

na vidhir naiva varṇaś ca na varjyāvarjyakalpanā|
na bhedo nidhanaṃ kiñcin nāśaucaṃ nodakakriyā5.54||

yogīśvareśvarasyaiva nityatṛptasya yoginaḥ|
citsvātmasukhaviśrāntibhāvalabdhasya puṇyataḥ||5.55||

samyaksvabhāvavijñānāt kramābhyāsān na cāsanāt|
na vairāgyān na nairāśyānāhāraprāṇadhāraṇāt||5.56||

na mudrādhāraṇad yogān na mānakarmasamāśrayāt|
na virakto vṛthāyāsān na kāyakleśadhāraṇāt||5.57||

na japān na tapodhyānān na yajñāt tīrthasevanāt|
na devārcanāśrayād bhaktyā nāśramāṇāñ ca pālanāt||5.58||

na ṣaḍdarśanakeśādidhāraṇān na ca muṇḍanāt|
nānantopāyayatnebhyaḥ prāpyate paramapadam||5.59||

etāni sādhanāni sarvāṇi daihikāni parityajya
paramapade 'daihike sthīyate siddhapuruṣair iti||5.60||

tat kathaṃ gurudṛkpātanāt prāyo dṛḍhānāṃ satyavādināṃ
sā sthitir jāyate||5.61||

kathanāc chaktipātād vā pādāvalokanāt|
prasādāt svaguroḥ samyak prāpyate paramaṃ padam||5.62||

na guror adhikaṃ na guror adhikaṃ na guror adhikaṃ na guror adhikam|
śivaśāsanataḥ śivaśāsanataḥ śivaśāsanataḥ śivaśāsanataḥ||5.63||

vāṅmātrād vātha dṛkpātāt yaḥ karoti ca tatkṣaṇāt|
praspuṭaṃ śāmbhavaṃ vedyaṃ svasaṃvedyaṃ paraṃ padam||5.64||

karuṇākhaḍgapātena chitvā pāśāṣṭakaṃ śi(po)śoḥ|
samyagānandajanakaḥ sadguruḥ so 'bhidhīyate||5.65||

nimiṣārdhārdhapātād vā yad vā pādāvalokanāt|
svātmānaṃ sthiram ādhatte tasmai śrīgurave namaḥ||5.66||

nānāvikalpaviśrāntiṃ kathayā kurute tu yaḥ|
sadguruḥ sa tu vijñeyo na tu mithyāviḍambakaḥ||5.67||

ata eva paramapadaprāptyarthaṃ sa sadguruḥ sadā
vandanīyaḥ gurur iti gṛṇāti śaṃ samyak caitanyaviśrāntim
upadiśati||
viśrāntyā svayam eva parāt paraṃ paramapadam eva
prasphuṭaṃ bhavati tatkṣaṇāt sākṣātkāro bhavati5.68||

ata eva mahāsiddhānāṃ mate proktam| vāgmātreṇa vā
dṛkpatamātreṇa vā samyag avalokanena vā
tatkṣaṇān muhur viśrāntimattāṃ nayatīti yaḥ sa sadgurur bhavati|
no cen nijaviśrāntiṃ vinā piṇḍapadayoḥ samarasakaraṇaṃ
na bhavatīti siddhāntaḥ| tasmān nijaviśrāntikārakaḥ
sadgurur abhidhīyate nānyaḥ||
punar vāgādiśāstradṛṣṭyānumānatas tarkamudrayā bhrāmiko
gurus tyājyaḥ5.69||

jñānahīno gurus tyājyaḥ mithyāvādī viḍambakaḥ|
svaviśrāntiṃ na jānāti pareṣāṃ sa karoti kim||5.70||

śilayā kiṃ paraṃ pāraṃ śilāsaṅghaḥ pratāryate|
svayaṃ tīrṇo bhaved yo 'sau parānnistārayatyalam||5.71||

vikalpasāgarād ghorāc cintākalloladustarāt|
prapañcavāsanāduṣṭa(garha)grāhajālasamākulāt||5.72||

vāsanālaharīvegād yaḥ svaṃ tārayituṃ kṣamaḥ|
svasthenaivopadeśena nirutthānena tatkṣaṇāt5.73||

tārayaty aiva dṛkpātāt kathanād vā vilokanāt|
tārite svapadaṃ dhatte svasvamadhye sthiro bhavet||5.74||

tataḥ sa mucyate śiṣyo janmasaṃsārabandhanāt|
parānandamayo bhūtvā niṣkalaḥ śivatāṃ vrajet||5.75||

kulānāṃ koṭikoṭīnāṃ tārayaty eva tatkṣaṇāt|
atas taṃ sadguruṃ sākṣāttrikālam abhivandayet||5.76||

sarvāṅgapraṇipātena stuvan nityaṃ guruṃ bhajet|
bhajanāt sthairyam āpnoti svasvarūpamayo bhavet5.77||

kim atra bahunoktena śāstrakoṭiśatena ca|
durlabhā cittaviśrāntir vinā gurukṛpāṃ parāṃ||5.78||

cittaviśrāntilabdhānāṃ yogināṃ dṛḍhacetasāṃ|
svasvamadhye nimagnanāṃ nirutthānaṃ viśeṣataḥ||5.79||

nimiṣāt prasphuṭaṃ bhāti durlabhaṃ paramaṃ padam|
yasmin piṇḍo bhavel līnāḥ sahasā nātra saṃśayaḥ||5.80||

saṃvitkriyāvikaraṇodayaḥcidvilolaviśrāntim eva
bhajatāṃ svayam eva bhāti|
graste svaveganicaye padapiṇḍam aikyaṃ satyaṃ bhavet  samarasaṃ
guruvatsalānām||5.81||

avadhūtayogī nāma ka ity apekṣāyām āha|
sa sarvān prakṛtivikārān avadhūnotītyavadhūtaḥ|
yogo 'syāstīti yogī| dhuñ kampane iti dhātuḥ kampanārthe vartate|
kampanaṃ cālanaṃ dehadaihikaṃ prapañcādiṣu viṣayeṣu saṃgataṃ
manaḥ parigṛhya tebhyaḥ prayāhṛtya svadhāmamahimni parilīnacetāḥ
prapañcaśūnya ādimadhyāntanidhanabhedavarjitaḥ||6.1||

6.2 yakāro vāyubījaṃ syād rakāro vahnibījakam|
tayor abheda oṃkāraś cidākāraḥ prakīrtitaḥ||6.2||

kleśapāśataraṅgāṇāṃ kṛntanena vimuṇḍanam|
sarvāvasthāvinirmuktaḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.3||

nijasmaravibhūtir yo yogī svāṅge vibhūṣitaḥ|
ādhāre yasya vāruḍhiḥ (ḍhaḥ) so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.4||

lokamadhye sthirāsīnaḥ samastakalanojjhitaḥ|
kaupinaṃ kharparo 'dainyaṃ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.5||

śaṃ sukhaṃ khaṃ paraṃ brahma śaṅkham saṃghaṭtanādbhavet|
siddhāntaṃ dhāritaṃ yena so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.6||

pādukā padasaṃvittir mṛgatvac mahāhatam|
velā yasya parā saṃvitso 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.7||

mekhalā nivṛttirnityaṃ svasvarūpaṃ kaṭāsanam|
nivṛttiḥ ṣaḍvikārebhyaḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.8||

citprakāśaparānandauyasya vai kuṇḍaladvayam|
japamālākṣaviśrāntiḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.9||

yasya dhairyamayo daṇḍaḥ parākāśaṃ ca kharparaṃ|
yogapaṭṭaṃ nijā śaktiḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.10||

bhedābhedau svayaṃ bhikṣāṃ ṣaḍrasāsvādane rataḥ|
jāraṇā(ta) tanmayībhāvaḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate6.11||

acintye nijadigdeśe svātantraṃ yas tu gacchati|
ekadeśāntarīyo yaḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.12||

svapiṇḍam amaraṃ kartum anantām amarīṃ ca yaḥ|
svayam eva pibed etāṃ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.13||

acintyaṃ vajravad gāḍhā vāsanāmalasaṃkulā|
sā vajrī bhakṣitā yena so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.14||

āvarttayati yaḥ samyak svasvamadhye svayaṃ sadā|
samatvena jagad vetti so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.15||

svātmānam avagacched yaḥ svātmāny evāvatiṣṭhate|
anutthānamayaḥ samyakso 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.16||

anutvā(tthā)dhārasampannaḥ pariviśrāntipāragaḥ|
dhṛticinmayatattvajñaḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.17||

avyaktaṃ vyaktam ādhatte vyaktaṃ sarvaṃ grasaty alam|
sva(sa)tyaṃ svāntare san yaḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.18||

avabhāsātmako bhāsaḥ svaprakāśe susaṃsthitaḥ|
lilayā ramate loke so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.19||

kva cid bhogī kva cit tyāgī kva cin nagnaḥ piśācavat|
kva cid rājā kva cācārī so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate||6.20||

evaṃvidhanānāsaṃketasūcakanityaprakāśe (vastuni)
sunijasvarūpī sarveṣāṃ siddhāntadarśanānāṃ
svasvarūpadarśane samyak sadvedhako 'vadhūtayogītyabhidhīyate
sa sadgururbhavati| yataḥ sarvadarśanānāṃ svasvarūpadarśane
samanvayaṃ karoti so 'vadhūtayogī syāt||6.21||

atyāśramī ca yogī ca jñānī siddhaśca suvrataḥ|
īśvaraśca tathā svāmī dhanyaḥ śrīsādhureva ca||

jitendriyaśca bhagavān sa sudhī kovido budhaḥ|
cārvākaścārhataśceti tathā bauddhaḥ prakāśāvit||6.22||

tārkikaśceti sāṅkhyaśca tathāmīmāṃsako viduḥ|
devatetyādividvadbhir kīrtitaḥ śāstrakoṭibhir||6.23||

ātmeti paramātmeti jīvātmeti punaḥ svayaṃ|
astitattvaṃ paraṃ sākṣacchivarudrādisaṃjñitaṃ||6.24||

śarīrapadmakuhare yatsarveṣāmavasthitaṃ|
tadavaśyaṃ mahāyāsādveditavyaṃ mumukṣubhiḥ||6.25||

brahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśca so 'kṣaraḥ paramaḥ svarāṭ|
sa eva indraḥ sa prāṇaḥ sa kālāgniḥ sacandrakaḥ
sa eva sūryaḥ sa śivaḥ sa eva paramaḥ śivaḥ|6.26||

sa eva yogagamyastu sāṅkhyaśāstraparāyaṇaiḥ||
sa eva karma ityktaḥ sarvakarmamīmāṃsakaiḥ|6.27||

sarvatra satparrananda ityukto vaidikairapi|
vyavahārairayaṃ bhedaḥ tasmātekasya nanyathā||6.28||

mudmodetu rānando (rānande)jīvātmaparamātmanoḥ
ubhayor aikyaṃ saṃvittir mudreti parikīrtitāḥ||6.29||

modante devasaṅghāś ca drāvante śurāśayaḥ|
mudreti kathitā sākṣāt sadā bhadrārthadāyinī||6.30||

asmin mārge 'dīkṣitā ye sadā saṃsārarāgiṇaḥ|
te hi pāṣaṇḍinaḥ proktāḥ saṃsāraparipelavāḥ||6.31||

avadhūtatanur yogī nirākārapade sthitaḥ|
sarveṣāṃ darśanānāṃ ca svasvarūpaṃ prakāśate||6.32||

sarvato bharitākāraṃ nijabodhena bṛṃhitaṃ|
carate brahmavidyas tu brahmacārī sa kathyate||6.33||

gṛhiṇī pūrṇatā nityā gehaṃ vyoma sadācalam|
yas tayor nivasaty atra gṛhasthaḥ so bhidhīyate||6.34||

sadāntaḥprasthito yo 'sau svaprakāśamaye vane|
vānaprasthaḥ sa vijñeyo na vane mṛgavac caran||6.35||

paramātmātha jīvātmā ātmany eva sphuraty alam|
tasmin nyastaḥ sadā yena saṃnyāsī so 'bhidhīyate||6.36||

māyākarmakalājālamaniśaṃ yena daṇḍitam|
acalo nagavadbhāti tridaṇḍī so 'bhidhīyate||6.37||

ekaṃ nānāvidhākāramasthiraṃ cañcalaṃ sadā|
taccittaṃ daṇḍitaṃ yena ekadaṇḍī sa kathyate||6.38||

śuddhaṃ śāntaṃ nirākāraṃ parānandaṃ sadooditam|
taṃ śivaṃ yo vijānāti śuddhabuddhaśaivo bhavet tu sa6.39||

saṃtāpayati dīptāni svendriyāṇi ca yaḥ sadā|
tāpasaḥ sa tu vijñeyo na ca gobhasmadhārakaḥ||6.40||

kriyājālaṃ paśuṃ hatvā patitvaṃ pūrṇatāṃ gatam|
yastiṣṭhetpaśubhāvena sa vai pāśupato bhavet||6.41||

parānandamayaṃ liṅgaṃ nijapīṭhe sadācale|
talliṅgaṃ pūjitaṃ yen sa vai kālamukho bhavet||6.42||

vilayaṃ sarvatattvānāṃ kṛtvā saṃdhāryate sthiram|
sarvadā yena vīreṇa liṅgadhārī bhavettu sa||6.43||

antarkādīni tattvāni tyaktvā nagno digambaraḥ|
yo nirvāṇapade līnaḥ sa nirvāṇaparo bhavet||6.44||

svasvarūpātmakaṃ jñānaṃ samantraṃ (samantāt) tatpratipālitum|
ananyatvaṃ sadā yena sa vai kāpāliko bhavet||6.45||

mahāvyāptiparaṃ tattvamādhārādheyavarjitam|
tadvrataṃ dhāritaṃ yena sa bhavedvai mahāvrataḥ||6.46||

kulaṃ sarvātmakaṃ piṇḍamakulaṃ sarvatomukham|
tayoraikyapadaṃ śaktiryas tāṃ veda sa śaktibhāk||6.47||

kaulaṃ sarvakalāgrāsaḥ sa kṛtaḥ satataṃ yayā|
tāṃ śaktiṃ vijānāti śaktijñānī sa kathyate ||6.48||

jñātvā kulākulaṃ tattvaṃ sa krameṇa krameṇa tu|
svaprakāśamahāśaktyā tataḥ śaktipadaṃ labhet||6.49||

mado madyaṃ matir mudrā māyā mīnaṃ manaḥ palam|
mūrcchanaṃ maithunaṃ yasya tenāsau śākta ucyate||6.50||

yayā bhāsasphuradrūpaṃ kṛtaṃ caiva sphuṭaṃ valāt|
tāṃ śaktiṃ yo vijānāti śāktaḥ so 'trābhidhīyate||6.51||

yaḥ karoti nirutthānaṃ kartṛcitprasaretsadā|
tadviśrāntistayā śaktyā śāktaḥ so 'trābhidhīyate||6.52||

vyāpākatve paraṃ sāraṃ yadviṣṇorādyamavyayaṃ|
viśrāntidāyakaṃ dehe tajjñātvā vaiṣṇavo bhavet||6.53||

bhāsvatsvarūpo yo bhedādbhedābhedabhavojjhitaḥ|
bhāti dehe sadā yasya sa vai bhāgavato bhavet||6.54||

yo vetti vaiṣṇavaṃ bhedaṃ sarvāsarvamayaṃ nijam|
prabuddhaṃ sarvadehasthaṃ bhedavādī bhavettu saḥ||6.55||

pañcānāmakṣayā hāniḥ (pañcānāmakṣapātānāṃ) pañcatvaṃ rātrirucyate|
tāṃ rātriṃ yo vijānāti sa bhavetpāñcarātrikaḥ||6.56||

yena jīvanti jīvā vaimuktiṃ yānti ca tatkṣaṇāt|
sa jīvo vidito yena sadājīvī sa kathyate||6.57||

yaḥ karoti sadā prītiṃ prasanne puruṣe pare|
śāsitanīndriyāṇyeva sāttvikaḥ so 'bhidhīyate||6.58||

sarvākāraṃ nirākāraṃ nirnimittaṃ nirañjanam|
sūkṣmaṃ haṃsaṃ ca yo vetti sa bhavetsūkṣmasāttvikaḥ||6.59||

satyamekamajaṃ nityamanantaṃ cākṣayaṃ dhruvam|
jñātvā yastu vadeddhīraḥ satyavādī sa kathyate||6.60||

jñāyajñeyamayābhyāṃ tu yoginaḥ svasvabhāvataḥ|
kalaṅkī sa tu vijñeyo vyāpakaḥ puruṣottamaḥ||6.61||

mukticāre matiryā vai vyāpikā svaprakāśikā|
eṣā jñānavatī yasya jñātāsau sātviko bhavet||6.62||

kṣapaṇaṃ cittavṛttīnāṃ rāgadveṣaviluṇṭhanam|
kurute vyomavan nagno yo śau kṣapaṇako bhavet||6.63||

prasaraṃ bhāsate śaktiḥ saṃkocaṃ bhāsate śivaḥ|
tayor yogasya kartā yaḥ sa bhavet siddhayogiraṭ||6.64||%from here first typed in by WJM

viśvātītaṃ yathā viśvam ekam eva virājate|
saṃyogena sadā yas tu siddhayogī bhavet tu saḥ||6.65||

sarvāsāṃ nijavṛttīnāṃ prasṛtir bhajate layam|
sa bhavet siddhasiddhānte siddhayogī mahābalaḥ||6.66||

udāsīnaḥ sadā śāntaḥ svastho 'ntarnijabhāsakaḥ|
mahānandamayo dhīraḥ sa bhavet siddhayogirāṭ||6.67||

paripūrṇaḥ prasannātmā sarvadā sarvapadoditaḥ|
viśuddho nirbharānandaḥ sa bhavet siddhayogirāṭ||6.68||

paripūrṇaḥ prasannātmā sarvānandakaraḥ sudhīḥ|
sarvānugrahadhīḥ samyak sa bhavet siddhayogirāṭ||6.69||

gate na śokaṃ vibhave na vāñchāṃ prāpte ca harṣaṃ na karoti yogī|
ānandapūrṇo nijabodhalīno na bādhyate kālapathena nityam||6.70||

evaṃ sarvasiddhāntadarśanānāṃ pṛthak pṛthag bhūtānām api brahmaṇi samanvayaśīlopadeśakarttā 'vadhūta eva sadguruḥ praśasyate||6.71||

eteṣām upadeśānāṃ sūcitānāṃ pṛthak pṛthak|
jāyate yasya viśrāntiḥ sa viśrānto 'bhidhīyate||6.72||

līnatāṃ ca svayaṃ yāti nirtthānacamatkṛte|
yato nirutthānamayāt so 'yaṃ syād avadhūtarāṭ||6.73||

tasmāt taṃ sadguruṃ sākṣād vandayet pūjayet sadā|
samyak siddhapadaṃ dhatte tatkṣaṇāt svātmabhāṣitam||6.74||

na vandanīyās te kāṣṭhāḥ darśanabhrāntikārakaḥ|
varjayet tān gurūn dūrād dhīraḥ siddhamatāśrayaḥ||6.75||

parapakṣanirāsaḥ kriyate

vedāntī bahutarkakarkaśamatir grastaḥ paraṃ māyayā
bhāṭṭāḥ karmaphalākulā hatadhiyo dvaitena vaiśeṣikāḥ||
anye bhedaratā vivādavikalāḥ sattattvato vañcitās
tasmāt siddhamataṃ svabhāvasamayaṃ dhīraḥ sadā saṃśrayet||6.76||

sāṃkhyā vaiṣṇavavaidikā vidhiparāḥ saṃnyāsinas tāpasāḥ
saurā vīraparāḥ prapañcaniratā baudhā jinaśrāvakāḥ||
ete kaṣṭaratā vṛthāpathagatāḥ sattattvato vañcitās
tasmāt siddhamataṃ svabhāvasamayaṃ dhīraḥ sadā saṃśrayet||6.77||

ācaryā bahudīkṣitā hutiratāḥ nagnavratās tāpasāḥ
nānātīrthaniṣevakā japaparā maune sthitā nityaśaḥ||
ete te khalu duḥkhabhāraniratā sattattvato vañcitās
tasmāt siddhamataṃ svabhāvasamayaṃ dhīraḥ sadā saṃśrayet||6.78||

ādau recakapūrakumbhakavidhau nāḍīpathaṃ śodhitaṃ
kṛtvā hṛtkamalodare tu sahasā cittaṃ mahāmūrchitam||
paścād avyayam akṣaraṃ parakule coṃkāradīpāṃkure
ye paśyanti samāhitena manasā teṣāṃ na nityaṃ padam||6.79||

cārvākāś caturāś ca tarkanipuṇā dehātmavāde ratās
te sarve na taranti duḥsahataraṃ ye te paraṃ sāttvikāḥ||
te sarve prabhavanti ye ca yavanāḥ pāpe ratā nirddayās
teṣām aihikam alpam eva hi phalaṃ tattvaṃ na mokṣapradam||6.80||

śrīhaṭṭe mastakānte tripuṭapuṭabile brahmarandhre lalāṭe
bhrūnetre nāsikāgre śravaṇapatharave ghaṇtikārājadante||
kaṇṭhe hṛnnābhimadhye trikamalakuhare coḍḍiyāṇe ca mūle
caivaṃ ye sthānalagnāḥ paramapadam aho nāsti teṣāṃ niruttham||6.81||

gollāṭe dīptipuñje pralayaśikhinibhe siddhajālandhare vā
śṛṃgāṭe jyotir ekaṃ taḍid iva taralaṃ brahmanāḍyantarāle||
bhālānte vidyudābhe tadupari śikhare koṭimārttaṇḍacaṇḍe
ye nityaṃ bhāvayante paramapadam aho nāsti teṣāṃ niruttham||6.82||

liṃgād daṇḍāṃkurāntarmanapavanagamād brahmanāḍyādibhedaṃ
kṛtvā binduṃ nayantaḥ paramapadaguhāṃ śaṃkhagarbhodarordhvam||
tatrāntarnādaghoṣaṃ gaganaguṇamayaṃ vajradaṇḍī krameṇa
ye kurvantīha kaṣṭāt paramapadam aho nāsti teṣāṃ niruttham||6.83||

samyak cālanadohanena satataṃ dīrghīkṛtāṃ lambikāṃ
tāṃ tālvantaraveśitāṃ ca daśamadvārodare śaṃkhinīm||
nītvā madhyamasandhisaṃghaṭaghaṭāt prāptāṃ śirodeśataḥ
pītvā ṣaḍvidhapānakāṣṭhitajanās tiṣṭhanti saṃmohitāḥ||6.84||

guhyāt paścimapūrvamārgam ubhayaṃ rudhvā 'nilaṃ madhyamaṃ
nītvā dhyānasamādhilakṣakaraṇair nānāsanābhyāsanaiḥ||
prāṇāpānasamāgamena satataṃ haṃsodare sadghaṭād
evaṃ ye 'pi bhajanti te bhavajale majjanty aho duḥkhitāḥ||6.85||

śaktyākuñcanam agnidīptikaraṇaṃ tv ādhārasaṃpīḍaṇāt
sthānāt kuṇḍalinīprabodhanam ataḥ kṛtvā tato mūrdhani||
nītvā pūrṇagiriṃ nipātanam adhaḥ kurvanti tasyāś ca ye
khaṇḍajñānaratās te nijapadaṃ teṣāṃ hi dūraṃ padam||6.86||

bandhaṃ bhedaṃ ca mudrāṃ galabilacibukāṃ baddhamārgeṣu vahniṃ
candrārkau sāmarasyaṃ śamadamaniyamān nādabindukalānte||
ye nityaṃ melayante hy anubhavamanasāpy unmanīyogayuktās
te lokān bhrāmayante nijasukhavimukhāḥ karmaduḥkhādhvabhājaḥ||6.87||

aṣṭāṃgaṃ yogamārgaṃ kulapuruṣamataṃ ṣaṇmukhīcakrabhedam
ūrdhvādhovāyumadhye ravikiraṇanibhaṃ sarvato vyāptisāram||
dṛṣṭyā ye vīkṣayante taralajalasamaṃ nīlavarṇaṃ nabho vā
evaṃ ye bhāvayante nigaditamatayas te 'pi hā kaṣṭabhājaḥ||6.88||

ādau dhāraṇaṃ śaṃkhadhāraṇam ataḥ kṛtvā mahādhāraṇaṃ
sampūrṇapratidhāraṇaṃ vidhibalād dṛṣṭiṃ tathā nirmalām||
ardholī bahulīha dṛṣṭāsanam atho ghaṇṭī vasan naulikā
ye kurvanti ca kārayanti ca sadā bhrāmyanti khidyanti te||6.89||

śaṃkhakṣālanam antaraṃ rasanayā tālvoṣṭhanāsārasaṃ
vānterulluṭhanaṃ kapāṭam amarīpānaṃ tathā kharparī||
vīryaṃ drāvitam ātmajaṃ punar aho grāsaṃ pralepaṃ ca vā
ye kurvanti jaḍās tu te na hi phalaṃ teṣāṃ tu siddhāntajam||6.90||

ghaṇṭākāhalakālamarddalamahābherīninādaṃ yadā
samyaṅ nādam anāhatadhvanimayaṃ śṛṇvanti caitādṛśam||
piṇḍe sarvagataṃ nirantaratayā brahmāṇḍamadhye 'pi vā
teṣāṃ siddhapadaṃ tataḥ samucitaṃ naivaṃ paraṃ labhyate||6.91||

vairāgyāt tṛṇaśākapallavajalaṃ kandaṃ phalaṃ mūlakaṃ
bhuktvā yo vanavāsam eva bhajate cā 'nye ca deśāntaram||
bālonmattapiśācamūkajaḍavac ceṣṭāś ca nānāvidhā
ye kurvanti padaṃ vinā matibalād bhraṣṭā vimuhyanti te||6.92||

kanthādhāraṇam adbhutaṃ bahuvidhaṃ bhikṣāṭanaṃ nāṭakaṃ
bhasmoddhūlanam aṃgakarkaśataraṃ kṛtvā 'tha varṣaṃ caran||
kṣetraṃ kṣetram aṭanti durgamataraṃ chitvā 'tha sarvendriyaṃ
no vindanti paraṃ padaṃ gurumukhād garveṇa kaṣṭāś ca te||6.93||

vāṇīṃ ca caturvidhāṃ svaracitāṃ siddhaiś ca vā nirmitāṃ
gāyatrīṃ ca paṭhanti pāṭhaniratā vidyāvivāde ratāḥ||
no vindanti tadartham ātmasadṛśaṃ khidyanti mohāc chalād
daṇḍaiḥ karttarīśūlacakralaguḍair bhāṇḍāś ca dṛṣṭāś ca te||6.94||

evaṃ śūnyādiśūnyaṃ paramaparapadaṃ pañcaśūnyādiśūnyaṃ
vyomātītaṃ hy anādyaṃ nijakulam akulaṃ cādbhutaṃ viśvarūpaṃ||
avyaktaṃ cāntarālaṃ nirudayam aparaṃ bhāsanirnāmam aikyaṃ
vāṅmātrād bhāsayanto bahuvidhamanaso vyākulā bhrāmitās te||6.95||

ājñāsiddhikaraṃ sadā samucitaṃ sampūrṇabhābhāsakaṃ
piṇḍe sarvagataṃ vidhānam amalaṃ siddhāntasāraṃ varam||
bhrānter nirharaṇaṃ sukhātisukhadaṃ kālāntakaṃ śāśvataṃ
tan nityaṃ kalanojjhitaṃ gurumayaṃ jñeyaṃ nirutthaṃ padam||6.96||

ātmeti paramātmeti jīvātmeti vicāraṇe|
trayāṇām aikyasambhūtir ādeśa iti kīrttitaḥ||6.97||

ādeśa iti sadvāṇīṃ sarvadvandvakṣayāpahām|
yo yoginaṃ prativadet sa yāty ātmānam aiśvaram||6.98||

āśādahanaṃ bhāsitaṃ kuṇḍalayugalaṃ vicārasantoṣaḥ|
kaupīnaṃ sthiracittaṃ kharparam ākāśam ātmano bhajanam||6.99||

etac chāstraṃ mahādivyaṃ rahasyaṃ pārameśvaram|
siddhāntaṃ sarvasārasya nānāsaṃketanirṇayam||6.100||

siddhānāṃ prakaṭaṃ siddhaṃ sadyaḥ pratyayakārakam|
ātmānandakaraṃ nityaṃ sarvasandehanāśanam||6.101||

na deyaṃ paraśiṣyebhyo nānyeṣāṃ sannidhau paṭhet|
na snehān na balāl lobhān na mohān nānṛtāc chalāt||6.102||

na maitrībhāvanād dānān na saundaryān na cāsanāt|
putrasyāpi na dātavyaṃ guruśiṣyakramaṃ vinā||6.103||

satyavanto dayācittā dṛḍhabhaktāḥ sadā 'calāḥ|
nistaraṃgā mahāśāntā sadā jñānaprabodhakāḥ||6.104||

bhayadainyaghṛṇālajjātṛṣṇāśāśokavarjitāḥ|
ālasyamadamātsaryadambhamāyāchalojjhitāḥ||6.105||

ahaṃkāramahāmoharāgadveṣaparāṅmukhāḥ|
krodhecchākāmanāsūyābhrāntilobhavivarjitāḥ||6.106||

niḥspṛhā nirmalā dhīrāḥ sadādvaitapade ratāḥ|
tebhyo deyaṃ prayatnena dhūrttebhyo gopayet sadā||6.107||

nindakā ye durācārāś cumbakāḥ gurutalpagāḥ|
nāstikā ye śaṭhāḥ krūrā vidyāvādaratās tathā||6.108||

yogācāraparibhraṣṭā nidrākalahayoḥ priyāḥ|
svasvakāryeṣu niṣṇātā gurukāryeṣu niḥspṛhāḥ|
etān vivarjayed dūre śiṣyatvenāgatān api||6.109||

sacchāstraṃ siddhamārgaś ca siddhasiddhāntapaddhatiḥ|
na deyā sarvathā tebhyo yadīcchec cirajīvanam|
gopanīyā prayatnena taskarebhyo dhanaṃ yathā||6.110||

teṣāṃ yo bodhayen mohād aparīkṣya tu mandadhīḥ|
na hi muktir bhavet tasya sadā duḥkhena sīdataḥ||6.111||

bhūcarī khecarī caiva śākinī ca niśācarī|
etāsām adbhutaṃ śāpaḥ siddhānāṃ bhairavasya ca|
mastake tasya patati tasmād yatnena rakṣayet||6.112||

gurupādāmbujasthāya parīkṣya pravadet sadā|
kuto duḥkhaṃ ca bhītiś ca tattvajñasya mahātmanaḥ||6.113||

kṛpayāiva pradātavyaṃ sampradāyapravṛttaye|
sampradāyapravṛttir hi sarveṣāṃ sammatā yataḥ||6.114||

māyāśaṃkaranāthāya natvā siddhāntapaddhatim|
likhitvā yaḥ paṭhed bhaktyā sa yāti paramāṃ gatim||6.115||

vidadhātv arthanicayaṃ bhaktānugrahamūrttimat|
smarānandabharaṃ ceto gaṇapatyabhidhaṃ mahaḥ||116||

||iti śrīgorakṣanāthakṛtau siddhasiddhāntapaddhatau avadhūtayogilakṣaṇo nāma ṣaṣṭhopadeśaḥ||
